{"tid":1546642,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】惠譽降香港信貸評級至AA 前景展望負面(勸告勇武停一停)","createTime":"2019-09-06T10:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T15:35:35.000Z","uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d7710f1cfd370ddea30122127464c99bff8d1d03","tid":1546642,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1567743903697&amp;issue=20190906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1567743903697%26issue%3D20190906&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=2a262dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1567743903697&amp;issue=20190906</a><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例】惠譽降香港信貸評級至AA 前景展望負面<br />\n<br />\n有D政府投資基金, 如果該地方一但跌到A+就唔可以投資.<br />\n政府話示威者,但邊個越攪越大件事,越來越多人受傷.<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為警察打到示威者重傷,真係外國唔可以理,<br />\n就好似國際評級機構會做野.<br />\n<br />\n勸告勇武停一停,同煲大惠譽降香港信貸評級影響.<br />\n有機會向德國交請願信.幫助示威者得到輕判(緩刑)<br />\n勇武停一停,有助德國幫手."},{"pid":"4f21c9dc2c3ca073dd3e1473a32babe8c3bccd79","tid":1546642,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=f8daf4e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"7c89bb52235b50ca06e93c1fa620e16b8e57ff5f","tid":1546642,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2d50e100c3afe78cf95fdb69d08e1ea37beda68","tid":1546642,"uid":226819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"有好多和你非活動，因為各自做，做咗都冇人知，唔夠noise<br />\n<br />\n例如零消費日，如果大家只係坐喺屋企無聲無息，noise唔大， 有冇人做，有幾多人做都唔知<br />\n<br />\n1. 我哋可以搞個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">零消費日集會</span></span></span></strong>，大家自備食物嘢餐又好，以物易物又好，集下氣，壯大聲勢，<br />\n<br />\n將呢個變成習慣同節目，如果零消費日就係坐喺屋企，好難持久<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋要制裁藍店， 同時都有支持黃店，可以搞組隊<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">支持黃店活動</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家集思廣益，俾下意見！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef99628d1c6ca4eff4295a1fb8689dd26d1c0e80","tid":1546642,"uid":69157,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"邏輯錯晒<br />\n唔係勇武邊有今日呀<br />\n停條撚 唔割呀 唔分化<br />\n全民都係勇武 你點解唔叫政府停一停 on9"},{"pid":"9a3f3b6201ad160820061fcb635b57a2786f1d25","tid":1546642,"uid":72381,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:59:09.000Z","msg":"打，往死裡打<br />\n黑警連信貸評級都打得低，警權無限大"},{"pid":"5144559b32b6bb65764a67d42ff65aea71ddc65c","tid":1546642,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"不推文呀大家<br />\n冷處理"},{"pid":"28385ed88a5071e67ccc2507113eb5591de83c94","tid":1546642,"